org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.host.tracker.rev140624.host

Interface AttachmentPoints

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<AttachmentPoints>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Host>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<AttachmentPointsKey>, org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.tbd.params.xml.ns.yang.network.topology.rev131021.TpAttributes

    public interface AttachmentPoints
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Host>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<AttachmentPoints>, org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.tbd.params.xml.ns.yang.network.topology.rev131021.TpAttributes, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<AttachmentPointsKey>
    the assumption is that all address can be reached at all attachment points

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module host-tracker-service 

     list attachment-points {
     key "tp-id"
     leaf tp-id {
         type tp-id;
     }
     leaf-list tp-ref {
         type tp-ref;
     }
     leaf corresponding-tp {
         type tp-ref;
     }
     leaf active {
         type boolean;
     }
     uses tp-attributes;
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is host-tracker-service/host/attachment-points

    To create instances of this class use AttachmentPointsBuilder.

    See Also:
    AttachmentPointsBuilder, AttachmentPointsKey
